      "acceptanceCriteria": "Ansys Mechanical version-controlled release with documented regression test suite; FDA in-house FEA code under 21 CFR Part 11 compliant version control.",
      "rationale": "All three FEA codes (FDA, Ansys, DePuy Synthes) operate under formal software quality management systems. Ansys is a commercially validated solver with published V&V documentation. FDA in-house code maintained under version control with audit trails. Required level 2 achieved."
    },
    {
      "factorStandard": "ASME-VV40-2018",
      "factorType": "Numerical code verification",
      "type": "CredibilityFactor",
      "requiredLevel": 2,
      "achievedLevel": 2,
      "factorStatus": "assessed",
      "acceptanceCriteria": "Benchmark problems with known analytical solutions solved to within 1% relative error for linear elastic beam bending and contact mechanics test cases.",
      "rationale": "Code verification performed using NAFEMS benchmark suite for linear elastic structural problems. Cantilever beam and Hertzian contact benchmarks reproduced within 0.6% of analytical solutions. Required level 2 achieved."
    },
    {
      "factorStandard": "ASME-VV40-2018",
      "factorType": "Discretization error",
      "type": "CredibilityFactor",
