      "factorStatus": "assessed",
      "acceptanceCriteria": "Validation scenario geometry, material, loading, and boundary conditions match COU within documented similarity bounds.",
      "rationale": "Validation activities performed on the identical screw geometry, material lot, and fixture configuration as the COU. The FEA model used for validation is the same model intended for COU predictions without modification. Validation scenario is directly representative of the COU; no extrapolation of validation evidence required. Required level 2 achieved."
    }
